68 private void PushParameters(IEnumerable<ParameterExpression> parameters)

70 foreach (ParameterExpression parameter in parameters)

1351 private bool TryPushLabelBlock(Expression node)
1352 {

1354 {
1355 default:
1356 if (_labelBlock.Kind != LabelScopeKind.Expression)
1357 {
1358 PushLabelBlock(LabelScopeKind.Expression);

1361 return false;

1368 return false;
